his bed in the ICU?

545
00:34:18,139 --> 00:34:20,725
What do you mean by that?

546
00:34:21,392 --> 00:34:23,770
I heard what the doctors said yesterday.

547
00:34:23,978 --> 00:34:25,730
I heard that

548
00:34:26,439 --> 00:34:29,567
you'd give my husband's operation
