800
00:52:15,298 --> 00:52:18,134
Stop it. You wouldn't attend it
even if you were invited.

801
00:52:18,218 --> 00:52:20,262
Invite me to see if I go or not.

802
00:52:20,345 --> 00:52:21,346
Pardon?

803
00:52:22,055 --> 00:52:24,015
